item.description:
Magic Hour is the fifth mini album by Kep1er. It will be released on September 25, 2023 with "Galileo" serving as the album's title track.



The physical album comes in 13 versions: Moonlighted, Sunkissed, Beloved, two Unit versions (Tape and Tropical Light), and nine individual Platform versions.

  2. "The Door"
  3. "Love on Lock"
